 | Image          = Vaginose-G15.jpg
 | Caption        = Micrograph of '''bacterial vaginosis''' — [[squamous cell]]s of the [[cervix]] covered with rod-shaped bacteria, ''[[Gardnerella vaginalis]]'' (arrows).
 | DiseasesDB     =
