      <text xml:space="preserve">{{about|the company|the Judas Priest album|British Steel (album)}}
{{Infobox Defunct Company 
| company_name = British Steel
| company_logo =[[File:British Steel.png|150px|British Steel company logo (1966–)]]
| fate = Merger
| successor = [[Corus Group|Corus]] 
| foundation = 1967
| defunct = 1999
| location = 
| industry = [[Steel]]
| key_people = 
| products = 
| num_employees = 
